            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數下跌-191.68點至6187.51點，跌幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間26日03:21，恆生科技指數下跌191.68點（或3%），暫報6187.51點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.72%</li><li>近 1 月：+9.51%</li><li>近 3 月：+19.04%</li><li>近 6 月：+15.62%</li><li>今年以來：+42.77%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大中華區概念領跌-3.19%。其中    ＸＬ二南方恒科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07226:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07226\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07226-HK</a>)            下跌        5.46%            ;        ＦＬ二南方國指(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07288:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07288\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07288-HK</a>)            下跌        4.07%            ;        ＸＬ二南方滬深三(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07233:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07233-HK</a>)            下跌        2.76%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>酒料飲料概念領跌-2.72%。其中    美捷滙控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01389:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01389\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01389-HK</a>)            下跌        13.85%            ;        怡園酒業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08146:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08146\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08146-HK</a>)            下跌        7.09%            ;        威揚酒業控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08509:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08509\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08509-HK</a>)            下跌        4.05%    。</p></section></main>",
